The paper focuses on developing a neural framework for collaborative filtering that leverages unstructured text data associated with items. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories related to information retrieval (cs.IR), machine learning (cs.LG), natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and databases (cs.DB).
